  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"x squared minus 5 x minus 24 equals 0\"><mrow>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<msup>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t<mn>2</mn>\n\t\t</msup>\n\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mn>5</mn>\n\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t<mn>24</mn>\n\t</mrow>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mn>0</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the sum of the solutions to the given equation?</p>",
